00028 /* these are the additional types needed to split out 64-vs-32-bit APIs  */
00029 /*                                                                       */
00030 
00031 /* The point of all of this is to avoid patching the existing smartcard
00032  * infrastructure (PC/SC Lite, libmusclecard+libmusclepkcs11 or CoolKey, any
00033  * other apps linking against any of these) because the need for patches
00034  * spreads without limit. The alternative is to patch the heck out of rdesktop,
00035  * which is already being done anyway.
00036  *
00037  * - jared.jennings@eglin.af.mil, 2 Aug 2006
00038  */
00039
